.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, tennis, golf, cricket, soccer
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, march, september, august, june
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: rowingmaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, reading, writinging, writing, sudoku
1. the british is the person who's sport is golf
2. the swedish is the person who's hobby is writinging
3. the danish is the person who's birthday is in august
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket
5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's birthday is in march
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's hobby is reading
7. the person who's sport is soccer is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing
11. the person who's hobby is sudokus is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the rowingmaster-smoker is the person who's birthday is in may
13. the german is the prince-smoker
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Sport		|    soccer	|     rowing	|      golf	|     tennis	|     cricket	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Hobby		|     singing	|    sudoku	|     reading	|     writing	|      writinging	|
| Birthday	|    june	|     august	|     september	|    march	|      may	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   rowingmaster	|
